<div class="nbunit" id="2Jul1938"><font color="red">2 July 1938</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): I have been out of town for a couple of days &hellip; this afternoon &hellip; found a packet of proof, typescript and a few pages of M.S. </div>
